e, or financial difficulties, that can induce a stress response in individuals.", "SOCIAL SUPPORT:Social support refers to the assistance and comfort provided by others, which can influence an individual's ability to cope with stress and reduce the impact of stressors.", "STRESSFUL LIFE EVENT:", "STRESS RELATED DISORDERS:A group of mental disorders primarily caused by psychological and social (environmental) factors, leading to abnormal psychological reactions, also known as reactive mental disorders. The condition is often short-lived and can resolve on its own. The total prevalence of reactive mental disorders in China was 0.068% in 1982, with the majority of cases occurring in young adults, though it can also affect adolescents and the elderly. The key characteristics include direct causation by psychosocial stress, clinical manifestations closely related to the stress factors, symptom resolution upon removal of the stressor, and a good prognosis without personality defects.", "PSYCHOSOCIAL STRESS:A type of stress caused by acute or prolonged psychological trauma or life events, which can be categorized into catastrophic events (e.g., natural disasters, accidents), life events (e.g., death of a loved one, unemployment), long-term psychological stress (e.g., family discord, work stress), and sudden environmental changes (e.g., imprisonment, migration).", "ACTH:Adrenocorticotropic hormone (ACTH) is released by the pituitary gland and stimulates the adrenal cortex to produce glucocorticoids during stress.", "GLUCOCORTICOIDS:Hormones produced by the adrenal cortex in response to ACTH stimulation, playing a key role in the body's stress response.", "IL-2:Interleukin-2 (IL-2) is an immune factor whose levels decrease during stress, affecting immune function.", "IL-6:Interleukin-6 (IL-6) is an immune factor whose levels increase during stress, affecting immune function.", "IGM:Immunoglobulin M (IgM) is an immune factor whose levels increase during stress, affecting immune function."], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}